<item>
 <title>Moodboards</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/co-design/tools/moodboards</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;Pictorial boards to illustrate work.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-stages field--type-taxonomy-term-reference field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;At what stage of the design process is the tool most useful?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/category/design-stages/define&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Define&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/category/design-stages/discover&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Discover&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-what field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Moodboards can help bring a piece of work to life through pictures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How do you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Used in the discover phase of the design process, a moodboard can be used as a way for the co-design team to get to know each other. Ask everyone to gather pictures of ‘things I like’ and stick them on their moodboard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Used in the define phase of the design process, a moodboard can help bring character profiles to life. After each member of the group has developed a profile, encourage them to create a moodboard to illustrate bits of the character.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-useful field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Useful resources when using the tool&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use art materials and magazines to create moodboards. Take photographs of the group’s moodboards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
